children.name: config
children.content:
[core]
	repositoryformatversion = 0
	filemode = false
	bare = true
	symlinks = false
	ignorecase = true
[remote "origin"]
	url = https://github.com/isomorphic-git/isomorphic-git.git
	fetch = +refs/heads/*:refs/remotes/origin/*
[remote "ssh"]
	url = git@github.com:isomorphic-git/isomorphic-git.git
	fetch = +refs/heads/*:refs/remotes/origin/*
